
** Current Version 5.5

*** Installation of the System

- Install developer version

- Disable Firewall and SELinux

- Change after the installation the ip-address to a address greater
  192.168.1.20, but see the other VMs

- Change the hostname in /etc/sysctl/network

- Add /etc/hosts entries for

  - ate
  - ovs
  - and the new VM

- Build emacs

  scp ovs:/OVS/tgz/emacs/emacs-23.2.tar.gz .
